</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Balsam_Fir_Christmas_Tree_Pruning.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a6/Balsam_Fir_Christmas_Tree_Pruning.jpg/220px-Balsam_Fir_Christmas_Tree_Pruning.jpg" width="220" height="165" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a6/Balsam_Fir_Christmas_Tree_Pruning.jpg/330px-Balsam_Fir_Christmas_Tree_Pruning.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a6/Balsam_Fir_Christmas_Tree_Pruning.jpg/440px-Balsam_Fir_Christmas_Tree_Pruning.jpg 2x" /></a>
