<li id="cite_note-AFP-16"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-AFP_16-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-AFP_16-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Shoemaker, Alfred Lewis. (1959) Christmas in Pennsylvania: a folk-cultural study. Edition 40. p.52,53. Stackpole Books 1999. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0811703282" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-8117-0328-2</a></span></li>
